OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BBC chairman Richard Sharp has resigned
OL,6, after a report found he did not        
OL,7, disclose potential perceived conflicts 
OL,8, of interest during his appointment.    
OL,10,FThe report looked at whether he was    
OL,11,Ftransparent about his involvement in   
OL,12,Fthe facilitation of a loan to Boris    
OL,13,FJohnson.                               
OL,15,FMr Sharp apologised, saying he did not 
OL,16,Fwant to be a distraction for the BBC.  
OL,18,FThe report, by barrister Adam          
OL,19,FHeppinstall, was published on Friday.  
